# AllFantasy Product Experience Requirements

## Landing page direction

Landing should be simple, high-conversion, mobile-first, and SEO/ASO aware.
Support:

- Light theme
- Dark theme
- AF Legacy theme
- English and Spanish toggle

Primary entry points:

1. Bracket Challenge
2. AF Fantasy Sports App
3. Legacy

Landing must include logo/crest, sign in, sign up, admin entry, and feature previews.
All CTA routing must be verified.

## Chat and social layer

Messaging should support:

- league chat
- direct messages
- group messages
- AI chat
- emojis, GIFs, attachments
- mentions, reactions, pins, polls

Moderation controls should support report, block, mute, suspension, and bans.

## Major tool experience

Maintain premium UX for:

- Trade Analyzer
- Waiver Wire
- Matchup Simulator
- Draft Room
- Bracket Challenge
- Tool Hub

Every major tool should include AI integration, sport awareness, mobile responsiveness, quick actions, and clean UI states.

## Admin and commissioner systems

Admin should cover users, leagues, moderation, analytics, feature toggles, and system health.
Commissioner controls should cover scoring, rosters, waivers, trades, draft settings, and announcements.
